<div class="title">DWAI that Should Have Been Avoided</div>
<div class="substance">Alcohol & Cannabis</div>
<div class="author">by <A HREF="exp.cgi?A=ShowAuthor&ID=107">Arjuna</A></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Arjuna. "DWAI that Should Have Been Avoided: An Experience with Alcohol & Cannabis (exp21827)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Mar 6, 2003. erowid.org/exp/21827</div>

<br/>



